caption:
I can't tell who's more excited about this, Maia or myself! #sponored The Graco EasyTurn 360 2-in-1 Convertible Car Seat is a game changer in our everyday life. Maia isn't getting any smaller and being able to turn the car seat outward is going to save my arms and back. Putting her in and taking her out has become so much easier and "fun" with the one handed rotating feature. I've always loved and trusted @graco and now it's amazing to see Maia love them and be so excited to ride in her car seat!🥰

#graco #safestplaceoutsideyourarms #paidpartnership
